                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="16180371" author="cziegeler" created="Tue, 26 Sep 2017 07:20:04 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ve changed the generator to use the l10n directory by default instead of the metatype directory for properties.&lt;br/&gt;
In addition if a module is using the metatype directory for properties the build will fail now. While this makes upgrading the plugin a little bit harder, it ensures that the spec is respected. And projects basically just need to rename their directory.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
